html.label: Intro
html.p:
Hello and welcome to our survey!
Thank you in advance for your participation. This study is very important to us and we ask that you answer each question carefully and completely.
While going through the survey, please use the scroll bar on the right and bottom of your screen to move up and down through questions and images. Please remember that there are no right or wrong answers. We are only interested in your opinions.
Thank you again! Let’s begin…

checkbox.label: S_PastParticipation
checkbox.title: Have you participated in a market research study within the past month, on any of the following topics?

pipe.label: continue_text
pipe.case: Please click the Continue button to proceed

html.label: Maximize
html.strong:
Throughout this survey, you are going to be shown several pictures. Please be sure that you maximize your window at this time, such that you can see these pictures with as much clarity as possible. You can also mouse over the images to see them magnified at any time.
Press F11 for full screen.

block.builder:title: Shopping Exercise

html.label: ShopIntro
html.span:
In a moment you will be redirected to a virtual shopping platform. [pipe:Pipe_Shelf_Txt]
Assume for a moment that you are doing your shopping for [pipe: Category]. Please select the products that you wish to purchase by clicking on the individual products on the shelf. You may purchase as many or as few products as you like.

ul.span: If you would like to see a close-up of a product, click on the product.
After you have selected a product, you may observe the structure and back of the package by using your mouse to rotate the product.
If you would like to purchase a product, click on the product and use the "add to basket" button and choose a quantity to add it to your cart.
When finished with the shopping trip, click the "checkout" button on the bottom of your screen.
You will have the opportunity to review your order and if everything is accurate please click the 'Finish Shopping' button.
Please be sure to view the entire shelf before proceeding.
